## Non-Negotiable Rules (Summary)

1. **Surfaces:** 5-level system (well 0.10 → void 0.13 → surface 0.18 → elevated 0.22 → raised 0.26). Lighter = closer. Minimum 0.04 gap between adjacent surfaces.
2. **Color:** OKLCH tokens only. `--stage-accent` is achromatic (white L=1.0). Only semantic status colors carry hue.
3. **Text:** Three tiers — primary L=0.88, secondary L=0.64 (WCAG AA), tertiary L=0.45 (disabled/decorative only).
4. **Motion:** Weight-based springs (STAGE_HEAVY/MEDIUM/LIGHT). No scale on hover. No bounce. Light-catch hover (+0.04 L brightness).
5. **Icons:** Lucide at `strokeWidth={1.5}`. Three color tiers matching text. Outline inactive, filled active for nav.
6. **Panels:** `StagePanel` or `stage-panel` class for new features. `liquid-card` / `glass-panel` for existing code during migration.
7. **Density:** `data-density="spacious|balanced|dense"`. All features available at all tiers. Density is presentation, not permission.
8. **Anti-patterns:** No `bg-white`, no `backdrop-blur` on content panels, no `rounded-3xl`, no chromatic accents, no `hover:scale`.

## Legacy Tokens (EXISTING CODE ONLY — Never Use in New Features)

These exist in unmigrated code. They are NOT acceptable for new features. If you encounter them, leave them unless the page is being actively migrated.

| Legacy (do NOT use in new code) | Stage Engineering replacement |
|---|---|
| `text-ceramic` | `text-[var(--stage-text-primary)]` |
| `text-ink-muted`, `text-mercury` | `text-[var(--stage-text-secondary)]` |
| `UNUSONIC_PHYSICS`, `FLUID_SPRING` | `STAGE_HEAVY` / `STAGE_MEDIUM` / `STAGE_LIGHT` |
| `liquid-card`, `glass-panel` | `stage-panel` class |
| `backdrop-blur` on panels | Solid `--stage-surface` background (no blur) |
| `neon-amber`, `neon-blue` as accent | `--stage-accent` (achromatic) or semantic status colors |
| `rounded-3xl`, `rounded-[28px]` | `var(--stage-radius-panel)` (density-aware) |
| `hover:scale`, `hover:brightness-110` | Light-catch hover (brightness shift only) |
